        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Water Quality Certification Improvement Act of 2021</b> </p> <p>This bill limits the authority of states with respect to water quality certifications. Specifically, the bill limits the authority of states to review federally permitted activities that may result in discharges into navigable waters.</p>]]>
        </text>
